      <title>俄罗斯补充预算在反嫁接驱动器中夺取财产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/russia-replenishes-budget-seizing-property-in-anti-graft-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据该国最高检察官称，去年俄罗斯法院去年没收了5000亿卢布（60亿美元）的财产。]]></description>
