    <item>
      <title>英国拒绝普京暂停对乌克兰的军事援助的要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/uk-rejects-putin-s-demand-to-suspend-military-aid-to-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府拒绝了俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）对乌克兰的盟友的要求，要求在任何停战期间将武器供应暂停给基辅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/uk-rejects-putin-s-demand-to-suspend-military-aid-to-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 13:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大人口增长会减慢临时居民镇压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/canada-population-growth-slows-on-temporary-resident-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于移民的下降，加拿大在三年内以最慢的速度增加了新的居民，这使大流行的人口繁荣繁重，使经济紧张，对新移民造成了公众的情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/canada-population-growth-slows-on-temporary-resident-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 13:06:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zelenskiy说他会在普京电话后与特朗普交谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/zelenskiy-says-will-talk-to-trump-on-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Volodymyr Zelenskiy表示，他将于周三与唐纳德·特朗普通过电话发言，这是美国总统与弗拉基米尔·普京的对话后的第二天，未能赢得俄罗斯对乌克兰30天停火的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/zelenskiy-says-will-talk-to-trump-on-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 10:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡尼的自由主义者在民意调查中激增，加拿大的当选即将开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/carney-s-liberals-surge-in-polls-with-canada-s-election-about-to-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着选民对贾斯汀·特鲁多（Justin Trudeau）的退出和马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）的崛起，在选举前夕，加拿大的自由党在选举前夕的一些民意调查中脱颖而出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/carney-s-liberals-surge-in-polls-with-canada-s-election-about-to-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其拘留了埃尔多安（Erdogan）的顶级竞争对手，引发了市场崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/turkish-police-detains-erdogan-rival-ekrem-imamoglu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其当局拘留了总统雷切普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）对腐败指控的最高政治竞争对手，后来在货币市场上进行了严重介入，以阻止该国多年来最糟糕的抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/turkish-police-detains-erdogan-rival-ekrem-imamoglu</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 04:52:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普批准了Venture Global的CP2项目的液化天然气出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-to-approve-lng-exports-from-venture-global-s-cp2-project</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的政府已批准了Venture Global LNG Inc.有条件的批准，将天然气从路易斯安那州计划的设施中出口，该机构在前总统乔·拜登（Joe Biden）的带领下停滞不前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-to-approve-lng-exports-from-venture-global-s-cp2-project</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 04:29:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，与加拿大的自由领导人打交道会更容易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-on-canada-elections-it-ll-be-easier-to-deal-with-liberal-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他宁愿与加拿大的自由党领导人合作，以解决他与渥太华煽动的贸易战，并权衡了邻国北美国家的一次预期民族大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-on-canada-elections-it-ll-be-easier-to-deal-with-liberal-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 01:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
